OOC: Yeah, its nice to have you back Megan, I hope everything is going
all right. Yan, what did you do to your fingers now?

BIC:

Cliffjumper kicks up a lot of dust, as he reaches the Maximal base,
followd by Beachcomber, Torcan, and Klant. He transforms and steps
forward. "Firedrill, we're going." He yells, his voice piercing the new
CF.

Firedrill looks at Iron Raptor and Prowl, worry filling his eyes, and
then wonder. He begins to walk out of the base, looking over his
shoulder to his if any Maximals noticed.
